snippet.title: Understanding Mephiston - (Blood Angels) 40k Lore
snippet.description:
Over 1 year ago I was watching the fantastic content by Vaatividya and came across the poem by Dylan Thomas 'Do not go gentle into that good night'. This completely changed my mind about the characters of the Blood Angels Chapter and truly helped me understand them much better. 

This Video contains spoilers and excerpts from the Blood Angels Omnibus, Sin of Damnation, Blood of Sanguinius, Revenant Crusade and City of Light. 

00:00 Introduction
01:10 Baal
08:41 Sin of Damnation
17:33 Black Rage
25:46 Rebirth
34:13 Indomitus
42:50 Primaris
51:23 The Journey

This video is an opinion editorial commentary.
